# Backend Documentation for AuditDNA Agricultural Compliance Platform

## Installation Instructions
1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/SeabassFather/audit-frontend.git
   cd audit-frontend
   ```
2. Install dependencies:
   ```bash
   npm install
   ```
3. Set up your environment variables. See the **Environment Variables** section for more details.
4. Start the server:
   ```bash
   npm start
   ```

## API Modules & Endpoints
### 1. User Management
- **POST** /api/users/register - User registration  
- **POST** /api/users/login - User login  
- **GET** /api/users/profile - Get user profile  

### 2. Compliance Check
- **POST** /api/compliance/check - Check compliance status  
- **GET** /api/compliance/history - Get compliance history  

### 3. Audit Management
- **POST** /api/audits/create - Create a new audit  
- **GET** /api/audits/:id - Get audit details  

### 4. Report Generation
- **POST** /api/reports/generate - Generate compliance report  
- **GET** /api/reports/:id - Get report details  

### 5. Notification Service
- **POST** /api/notifications/send - Send notifications  
- **GET** /api/notifications/history - Get notification history  

### 6. Payment Processing
- **POST** /api/payments/submit - Submit payment  
- **GET** /api/payments/:id - Get payment details  

### 7. Document Management
- **POST** /api/documents/upload - Upload document  
- **GET** /api/documents/:id - Get document details  

### 8. Reporting Dashboard
- **GET** /api/dashboard/summary - Get dashboard summary  
- **GET** /api/dashboard/details - Get detailed report  

### 9. User Feedback
- **POST** /api/feedback/submit - Submit feedback  
- **GET** /api/feedback/history - Get feedback history  

### 10. Integration Manager
- **POST** /api/integrations/setup - Setup integration  
- **GET** /api/integrations/status - Get integration status  

### 11. Data Export
- **POST** /api/data/export - Export data  
- **GET** /api/data/download/:id - Download exported data  

